            "text": "In this technical guide, we focus on BGE M3 retrieval, a high-performance embedding model designed for efficient information retrieval in API-driven systems. This post provides actionable insights for experienced API teams to deploy and optimize BGE M3 in production, emphasizing practical implementation over theory."
