            "type": "text",
            "text": "Core Concepts of BGE M3 Retrieval"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "BGE M3 retrieval leverages the Bge_M3_FP16 model, which uses FP16 precision to balance accuracy and computational efficiency. Key aspects include its multi-vector representation for dense retrieval, support for long-context inputs, and compatibility with common API frameworks. Understanding these fundamentals is crucial for integrating the model into retrieval pipelines, such as those for semantic search or recommendation systems."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Configuration and Optimization for Production"
