        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To optimize BGE M3 retrieval for production, configure the model with appropriate parameters. Use batch processing to maximize throughput, and set the FP16 precision to reduce memory footprint without significant accuracy loss. Example API call snippet:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
